23
00:03:19,939 --> 00:03:21,167
Bola ao ar.

24
00:03:22,876 --> 00:03:24,274
Artie Coogan.

25
00:03:25,011 --> 00:03:28,105
- O quê?
- Artie Coogan, é isso.

26
00:03:28,314 --> 00:03:29,439
É.

27
00:03:30,749 --> 00:03:32,045
Artie, louco Artie.

28
